claim.claim-text:
The current transformer (CT) system of claim 1, wherein each of the sensor CT and the generator CT comprises:
a top assembly in which a core and a coil are installed;
a bottom assembly corresponding to the top assembly;
a hinge to which the top assembly and the bottom assembly are rotatably coupled; and
a lock clip selectively opening and closing the top assembly and the bottom assembly.

